dragons who used it to nest, easily accomodating a she-dragon and her mate.
Debris from the carvings lay all about, used to build up the wall that
incubates the eggs, then broken down again when the hatchlings make their way
to daylight.  A shimmering silt covers the ground.

name: End of a Large Cavern
description:
Egg shell shards litter the ground, shimmering like the silt covered ground.
Upon closer inspection, you realize that the shells and silt are solid gold
created from hatchling fire as they dry their wings or try to make a meal of
one another before the outer wall is broken down.

name: End of a Large Cavern
description:
Egg shell shards litter the ground, shimmering like the silt covered ground.
Upon closer inspection, you realize that the shells and silt are solid gold
created from hatchling fire as they dry their wings or try to make a meal of
one another before the outer wall is broken down.

name: A Large Cavern
description:
Sculpted by a river long past, the cave was made larger by the claws of the
dragons who used it to nest, easily accomodating a she-dragon and her mate.
Debris from the carvings lay all about, used to build up the wall that
incubates the eggs, then broken down again when the hatchlings make their way
to daylight.  A shimmering silt covers the ground.

name: A Precarious Path
description:
Debris from the eroding canyon makes traversing the narrow pathways zig-
zagging the cliff walls difficult at the best of times and almost impossible
where the paths have nearly crumbled away.  Slipping and sliding as you make
your way around, you desperately look for handholds to help you retain your
balance.

name: A Precarious Path
description:
Loose stones shift precariously beneath your feet, causing you to struggle
to retain your balance.  At times, the ledge is so narrow you find yourself
crawling on your hands and knees just to avoid falling down the sheer, cliff
wall to the rock strewn desert below.

name: End of a Large Cavern
description:
Egg shell shards litter the ground, shimmering like the silt covered ground.
Upon closer inspection, you realize that the shells and silt are solid gold
created from hatchling fire as they dry their wings or try to make a meal of
one another before the outer wall is broken down.

created from hatchling fire as they dry their wings or try to make a meal of
one another before the outer wall is broken down.

description:

created from hatchling fire as they dry their wings or try to make a meal of
one another before the outer wall is broken down.

name: A Precarious Path
description:
Debris from the eroding canyon makes traversing the narrow pathways zig-
zagging the cliff walls difficult at the best of times and almost impossible
where the paths have nearly crumbled away.  Slipping and sliding as you make
your way around, you desperately look for handholds to help you retain your
balance.

name: Entrance to a Large Cavern
description:
Built up and torn down again over and over by hatchling dragon fire, the
cavernous space is large enough to comfortably hold a female dragon ready to
lay her eggs.  Large boulders, blackened from the fires, are strewn across the
pathway, partially blocking the entrance to the cave, which reverbrates with
each little sound.  With a sense of trepedition, you wonder if the occupants
are currently in residence.

created from hatchling fire as they dry their wings or try to make a meal of
one another before the outer wall is broken down.

name: On a woodland trail
description:
You stand on a narrow but well kept trail through the thick woods. The
sounds of animals resound all about you and leaves rustle softly in the wind.
Above you the high tree top canopy blocks out much of the sun, making the
region seem darker than it really is. A dirt path heads westwards into the
region.

name: On a woodland trail
description:
You stand on a narrow but well kept trail through the thick woods. The
sounds of animals resound all about you and leaves rustle softly in the wind.
Above you the high tree top canopy blocks out much of the sun, making the
region seem darker than it really is. The dirt pathway heads west and east.

name: On a woodland trail
description:
You stand on a narrow but well kept trail through the thick woods. The
sounds of animals resound all about you and leaves rustle softly in the wind.
Above you the high tree top canopy blocks out much of the sun, making the
region seem darker than it really is. The dirt path turns north and east.

name: On a woodland trail
description:
You stand on a narrow but well kept trail through the thick woods. The
sounds of animals resound all about you and leaves rustle softly in the wind.
Above you the high tree top canopy blocks out much of the sun, making the
region seem darker than it really is. The dirt path continues north and south.

name: On a woodland trail
description:
You stand on a narrow but well kept trail through the thick woods. The sounds
of animals resound all about you and leaves rustle softly in the wind. Above
you the high tree top canopy blocks out much of the sun, making the region
seem darker than it really is. The dirt path continues north where it curves
west, and south.

name: A turn in the woodland trail
description:
The trail curves west and south here. The droppings of animals and the
signs of frequent passage by them is an indication that this region is
safer than the dark shadows covering it suggest.

name: On a woodland trail
description:
You stand on a narrow but well kept trail through the thick woods. The sounds
of animals resound all about you and leaves rustle softly in the wind. Above
you the high tree top canopy blocks out much of the sun, making the region
seem darker than it really is. The dirt path continues north and east.

name: A T-junction in the woodland trail
description:
You stand on a narrow but well kept trail through the thick woods. The sounds
of animals resound all about you and leaves rustle softly in the wind. Above
you the high tree top canopy blocks out much of the sun, making the region
seem darker than it really is. To the west you can hear faint sounds of
running water and the noises of people. The path continues north and south.

name: On a woodland trail
description:
You stand on a narrow but well kept trail through the thick woods. The sounds
of animals resound all about you and leaves rustle softly in the wind. Above
you the high tree top canopy blocks out much of the sun, making the region
seem darker than it really is. The path continues north and south.

name: On a woodland trail
description:
You stand on a narrow but well kept trail through the thick woods. The sounds
of animals resound all about you and leaves rustle softly in the wind. Above
you the high tree top canopy blocks out much of the sun, making the region
seem darker than it really is. To the west the path heads onto a small bridge
over a river, while to the south it leads off into the woods.

name: On a small wooden bridge
description:
You are standing on a small bridge leading across a deep running river. Loud
gurgling water rushes beneath you and froths up along the river banks. Off to
the south you can make out a small lake where the river ends, and to the west
you can see buildings of some sort nestled between this bridge and one further
on.

name: Southern outskirts of Greenleaf dale
description:
You stand amidst a small cluster of buildings between two bridges. The woods
around you are thick and well kept, showing very little sign of human ruin
that normally accompanies human settlement. To the north you can see a small
house and south is what looks like a guard outpost. The path heads east across
a bridge and westwards into Greenleaf dale.

name: Southern outskirts of Greenleaf dale
description:
You stand amidst a small cluster of buildings between two bridges. The woods
around you are thick and well kept, showing very little sign of human ruin
that normally accompanies human settlement. To the north you can see a small
house. The path heads east and west amongst the buildings.

name: Southern outskirts of Greenleaf dale
description:
You stand amidst a small cluster of buildings between two bridges. The woods
around you are thick and well kept, showing very little sign of human ruin
that normally accompanies human settlement. To the north and south you can see
a pair of small houses. The path heads east amidst the buildings, and west
across a small bridge.

name: On a small wooden bridge
description:
You are standing on a small bridge leading across a deep running river.
Loud gurgling water rushes beneath you and froths up along the river
banks. To the north you can make out a town of somesort, while to the east
is a bridge leading to a small cluster of buildings. The path heads east
over the bridge, and west towards the township.

name: On a the woodland trail
description:
You stand on a well travelled dirt pathway through a thick forest. The
region is dark from the choking tree canopy but it is a dark that is
comforting rather than menacing. To the east is a small bridge leading to
some building, while the path heads west to a bend.

name: A bend in the woodland path
description:
You are at a sharp bend in the path through the woods. It heads north towards
some buildings and more cultivated land, or east into the woods and a small
bridge further off.

name: A path in the woodlands
description:
You are on a path through some thick woodland forest. Although the region is
dark from the overhanging tree cover you can still make out the well used path
with little problem. Northwards you can see buildings, while south the path
heads into a bend.

name: At the entrance to Greenleaf dale
description:
You stand at the entrance to a small township. The thick and dark forest
around it seems strangely comforting, like a protective shell from the
rest of the harsh world. To the east you can see a small house of some
local resident. The path heads northwards into the township or south into
the surrounding forests.

name: A pathway through the township
description:
You are walking on a well kept and regularly frequented path through the
small township here in the forest. The air is fresh and there is an
unexplainable feeling of peace from all around. To the east and west lie
small houses, while the path leads north to a common square and south out
of the town.

name: At a common square in the township
description:
You stand within a large open gravel square set aside for the town's
way-point. Signs and small makeshift stalls line the intersecting paths as
people try to make the most of the busy and industrius crossing. The path
continues north and south through the township. Eastwards you can see the
majority of the town buildings and what looks like a market place, and
west appears to head off into some fields.

name: A pathway through the township
description:
You are walking on a well kept and regularly frequented path through the small
township here in the forest. The air is fresh and there is an unexplainable
feeling of peace from all around. To the east lies a small house, while
the path leads north out of the town or south to a common square.

name: A pathway through the township
description:
You are walking on a well kept and regularly frequented path through the small
township here in the forest. The air is fresh and there is an unexplainable
feeling of peace from all around. To the east and west lie small houses, while
the path leads north out of the town, or south into it.

name: A pathway through the township
description:
You are walking on a well kept and regularly frequented path through the small
township here in the forest. The air is fresh and there is an unexplainable
feeling of peace from all around. For some reason the path is not quite so
well travelled this far north of the town. The path leads north out of the
town, or south into it.

name: The northern outskirts of Greenleaf dale
description:
You stand on a small pathway at the northern end of a small township. Around
you the forest is thick and dark, covered in flickering shadows. The pathway
here is not too well defined and shows an evident lack of use. The path leads
east out of the town, or south towards it.

name: The northern outskirts of Greenleaf dale
description:
You stand on a small pathway at the northern end of a small township. Around
you the forest is thick and dark, covered in flickering shadows. The pathway
here is not too well defined and shows an evident lack of use. The path leads
east and west.

name: The northern outskirts of Greenleaf dale
description:
You stand on a small pathway at the northern end of a small township. Around
you the forest is thick and dark, covered in flickering shadows. The pathway
here is not too well defined and shows an evident lack of use. The path leads
west back to the town, or north towards a small cluster of isolated buildings.

name: The northern outskirts of Greenleaf dale
description:
You stand on a small pathway at the northern end of a small township. Around
you the forest is thick and dark, covered in flickering shadows. The pathway
here is not too well defined and shows an evident lack of use. To the east and
west are small buildings, while the path itself leads north and south.

name: The northern outskirts of Greenleaf dale
description:
You stand on a small pathway at the northern end of a small township. Around
you the forest is thick and dark, covered in flickering shadows. The pathway
here is not too well defined and shows an evident lack of use. To the east and
west are small buildings, while the path itself leads north and south.

name: The northern outskirts of Greenleaf dale
description:
You stand at the very northern end of what could possibly be called the
township. Even here there is more forest than civilised land and the trees
seem darker and more intimidating than elsewhere. To the south lies a small
cluster of buildings, and eastwards the forest grows thicker and darker.

name: A pathway through the township
description:
You stand upon a well kept gravel path. Around you the thick forest
provides a comforting cover from the rest of the world, and soft noises of
animals can be heard. To the north is a small building labelled 'customs'.
East of here the path heads towards the main township, while west there is
a large common square.

name: Within the main township
description:
You stand amongst small buildings in the township of Greenleaf dale. Trees
line the pathway all around you and it almost seems like you are within a
forest rather than a town. To the north and south are small houses, and to
the east there is a large open market place. West leads back out of the
main township.

name: NW corner of the Dale market
description:
You stand within a bustling market place filled with the sounds of
commerce and everyday living. Smells of sweet meets and bread waft through
the air and music can be heard from somewhere nearby. To the north there
is a baker's shop from which the smells of fresh bread are coming. West is
a small tavern filled with drunken laughter.

name: Northern end of the Dale Market
description:
You stand within a bustling market place filled with the sounds of
commerce and everyday living. Smells of sweet meets and bread waft through
the air and music can be heard from somewhere nearby. To the north is a
large inn filled with happy partons.

name: NE corner of the Dale market
description:
You stand within a bustling market place filled with the sounds of
commerce and everyday living. Smells of sweet meets and bread waft through
the air and music can be heard from somewhere nearby. North of here is a
loud armorer's shop and east is an accompanying weaponsmith.

name: Western side of the Dale market
description:
You stand within a bustling market place filled with the sounds of
commerce and everyday living. Smells of sweet meets and bread waft through
the air and music can be heard from somewhere nearby. The market spreads
out to the north, east and south. A small pathway heads west out of the
main market.

name: Centre of the Dale market
description:
You stand within the centre of the township's main trading square. All
around you people are busy buying goods and talking to neighbours. Loud
sounds and strong smells greet you at every turn and assault your senses.
All around you the market spreads out.

name: Eastern side of the Dale market
description:
You stand within a bustling market place filled with the sounds of
commerce and everyday living. Smells of sweet meets and bread waft through
the air and music can be heard from somewhere nearby. The market heads off
to the north,south and west. To the east lies a wide path heading towards
what look like houses.

name: SW corner of the Dale market
description:
You stand within a bustling market place filled with the sounds of
commerce and everyday living. Smells of sweet meets and bread waft through
the air and music can be heard from somewhere nearby. To the south is a
strange shop with a sign bearing a crescent moon. West is a shop selling
forest clothing for the local hunters and trappers.

name: Southern end of the Dale market
description:
You stand within a bustling market place filled with the sounds of
commerce and everyday living. Smells of sweet meets and bread waft through
the air and music can be heard from somewhere nearby.

name: SE corner of the Dale market
description:
You stand within a bustling market place filled with the sounds of
commerce and everyday living. Smells of sweet meets and bread waft through
the air and music can be heard from somewhere nearby. You can see a bank
to the east and a busy clothing shop to the south.

name: On a pathway amidst the Dale community
description:
You are standing upon a wide gravel pathway through the eastern side of the
forest township. Thick woods surround you in a strangely comforting
cover, and animals can occasionally be seen loitering near the edges of
the town. To the north is a small house, and more can be seen in clusters
to the east. West of here is what looks like a market place.

name: On a pathway amidst the Dale community
description:
You are standing upon a wide gravel pathway through the eastern side of
the forest township. Thick woods surround you in a strangely comforting
cover, and animals can occasionally be seen loitering near the edges of
the town. To the north and south are some small houses, and to the east
are clusters of more houses.

name: On a pathway amidst the Dale community
description:
You are standing upon a wide gravel pathway through the eastern side of the
forest township. Thick woods surround you in a strangely comforting
cover, and animals can occasionally be seen loitering near the edges of
the town. To the north is a guard headquarters and south is a small house.
The pathway heads east and west.

name: End of the township
description:
You are standing at the eastern edge of the Greenleaf dale community.
Thick woods surround you and enclose the buildings in a smothering
embrace. A large temple has been erected to the north, and south is a
grand house of some regional lord. The path heads back west to a large
cluster of common houses.

name: Foyer of the Lord's Manor
description:
You stand within a rich and elegant house. The walls are solid and even this
close to the main dale market you can barely hear anything outside the house.
A staircase heads up into the house, and a door opens out north to the dale's
main streets.

name: In a large house
description:
You stand in the house of a very rich, very powerful member of the dale
community. The furnishings are the finest in the region and the food that
has been laid out on the table is superbly prepared. A staircase leads
down and a door leads east. To the west the house opens out onto a
balcony.

name: Inside the temple of Sun
description:
You are at the entrance to a fine, well built temple. Symbols of sun and
prosperity have been carved into the walls, along with markings to drive
away evil spirits and curses. To the east is a small alcove, while the
main temple heads north to the altar room.

name: The altar room
description:
This is where the dale community gathers to worship. The room is plain and
nodescript, holding to the value of humility. There are doors to the east
and west.

name: The Green Fletcher's Tavern
description:
The tavern is noisy and messy. It looks like much of what is served here
ends up on the floor rather than in the customer's stomachs. To the east
lies the dale market square.

name: The Baker's Delight
description:
This bakery has the warm smell of fresh bread and other savoury delights.
Rows of cakes also line the service table and make your mouth water. To
the south lies the dale market square.

name: The Shadowdale Armory
description:
The room is noisy, smelly and hot. A typical armory if ever you've seen one.
Yet this one seems somewhat more professional than the regular midgaard run
of the mill blackmsith.

name: The Worthy Weapons shop
description:
The smell of burning metals and hot coals assaults you as you enter this
shop. The place is very well set up, however, and looks quite professional.

name: The Dale Bank
description:
This branch of the Shalaran banks is small and seems a little unsafe to be
holding such large sums of money. Maybe the magical wards placed around
it by the local archmagi have something to do with it's security.

name: Wear 'N Tear
description:
This shop is in disarry. It seems to be newly opened and has little stock
of interest right now. Perhaps in time it will get more organised and
open.

name: The Crescent Moon
description:
You find yourself standing in a weird and cluttered little shop. Odds and
ends of all sorts lie around the room, most of which look quite useless.
But maybe there is one or two things which may actually have some use..

name: Forest Wear
description:
You are standing within a building that has been made, quite convincingly,
to look like a forest cabin. It seems to be a place where local trappers
and hunters can come to buy clothing to help them find their prey a little
easier. The clothes themselves seem a little flimsy for fighting in, but
well made nonetheless.

name: The Quartermaster's Hold
description:
You are standing in what looks like an official's room with maps and
charts designed to guide people to where they should be guided. There is a
door leading back south.

name: A small house
description:
You find yourself within a small but tidy house. The main room is large
and comfortable with a homely feeling about it. Small partitions seperate
the house into bedrooms and a couple of windows are set into the sides to
provide a view of the beautiful forests. There is a door leading south out
of the house.

name: A small house
description:
You find yourself within a small but tidy house. The main room is large
and comfortable with a homely feeling about it. Small partitions seperate
the house into bedrooms and a couple of windows are set into the sides to
provide a view of the beautiful forests. There is a door leading north out
of the house.

name: A small house
description:
You find yourself within a small but tidy house. The main room is large
and comfortable with a homely feeling about it. Small partitions seperate
the house into bedrooms and a couple of windows are set into the sides to
provide a view of the beautiful forests. There is a door leading south out
of the house.

name: A small house
description:
You find yourself within a small but tidy house. The main room is large
and comfortable with a homely feeling about it. Small partitions seperate
the house into bedrooms and a couple of windows are set into the sides to
provide a view of the beautiful forests. There is a door leading south out
of the house.

name: A small house
description:
You find yourself within a small but tidy house. The main room is large
and comfortable with a homely feeling about it. Small partitions seperate
the house into bedrooms and a couple of windows are set into the sides to
provide a view of the beautiful forests. There is a door leading north out
of the house.

name: A small house
description:
You find yourself within a small but tidy house. The main room is large
and comfortable with a homely feeling about it. Small partitions seperate
the house into bedrooms and a couple of windows are set into the sides to
provide a view of the beautiful forests. There is a door leading north out
of the house.

name: The guard headquarters
description:
This room is a sparse and uncomfortable guardhouse. It seems mostly that
the locals provide the guard force here and they tend to live at home
anyway.

name: The Lord Templar's Room
description:
Beautiful plaques and rugs adorn this room making it seem more like a
room of a prince than a humble servant of god. Yet the richness is surely
well deserved or the dale people would hardly provide for such a man.

name: The High Cleric's Chamber
description:
A very spartan and homely room. This has only the bare minimums for
living in. A bed, desk and a window are the only items and they seem more
for function than aesthetics.

name: A small alcove in the temple
description:
You stand in a small side room of the temple where holy water has been
set aside for those wishing to bless themselves before seeing the priest.

name: On a balcony overlooking the Dale
description:
You stand upon a high wooden balcony set high above the house. From here
the view is superb and allows you to glimpse much of the dale that was
hidden by the thick woods surrounding it. Far off in the west you can make
out fields and way off in the north is a dark ominous forest. The only
exit is back east into the house.

name: The Lord's Private Study
description:
You are standing within a rich and luxurious study. Much of it contains
papers and documents relating to the governing of the propsperous daleland
town and it is evident the lord takes his duties seriously.

name: A pathway through the township
description:
You stand upon a well kept gravel path. Around you the thick forest
provides a comforting cover from the rest of the world, and soft noises of
animals can be heard. To the north is a small building, while east there
is a large common square.

name: A pathway through the township
description:
You stand upon a well kept gravel path. Around you the thick forest
provides a comforting cover from the rest of the world, and soft noises of
animals can be heard. To the north and south are some houses, while the
pathway heads east and west.

name: A pathway through the western outskirts of Shadowdale
description:
You stand upon a well kept gravel path. Around you the thick forest
provides a comforting cover from the rest of the world, and soft noises of
animals can be heard. The gravel path continues east and west.

name: Outside the western outskirts of Shadowdale
description:
You stand upon a well kept gravel path. Around you the thick forest
provides a comforting cover from the rest of the world, and soft noises of
animals can be heard. The gravel path leads north towards some cultivated
fields, and east to some houses.

name: The western outskirts of Shadowdale
description:
You stand upon a well kept gravel path. Around you the thick forest
provides a comforting cover from the rest of the world, and soft noises of
animals can be heard. The gravel path leads north towards some cultivated
fields, or south.

name: A small house
description:
You find yourself within a small but tidy house. The main room is large
and comfortable with a homely feeling about it. Small partitions seperate
the house into bedrooms and a couple of windows are set into the sides to
provide a view of the beautiful forests. There is a door leading west out
of the house.

name: Before the dale fields
description:
You are standing before some well cultivated fields. Small trails wind
between them where farmers have trodden in order to tend and harvest their
crops. The trails lead east and west through the fields, and a larger
gravel pathway heads south away from the farming land.

name: In the dale fields
description:
You stand amidst well kept farm fields filled with various crops and fruits.
Long rows of vegetables have been planted side by side between small trails
to allow easy harvesting. The fields continue north and west.

name: In the dale fields
description:

Long rows of vegetables have been planted side by side between small trails
to allow easy harvesting. The fields continue north and east.

description:
You stand at the edge of a large lake amidst the dale farm fields. Water has
been diverted from it to form shallow riverlets to water the crops. All about
you the fields spread out.

description:
You stand amidst well kept farm fields filled with various crops and fruits.
Long rows of vegetables have been planted side by side between small trails
to allow easy harvesting. The fields continue south and west. To the east the
trails lead off into a small grove of trees amidst the surrounding forest.

name: On the edge of a grove
description:
You are standing at the very edge of a small grove of trees amidst the forest
surrounding the dale. To the west the local farm fields lay spread out, and
to the east the grove continues into the forests.

name: On a path in the northern dale
description:
You are standing at the very northern end of the dale. All around you the
forest looms forebodingly and cloaks everything in shadows. East of here you
can make out a dense and dark forest.

name: A path through the forest
description:
You stand on a narrow but well kept trail through the thick woods. The sounds
of animals resound all about you and leaves rustle softly in the wind. Above
you the high tree top canopy blocks out much of the sun, making the region
seem darker than it really is. To the west you can hear the faint sounds of
water splashing. The path leads into a T-junction to the east.

name: A muddy path through the forest
description:
You are on a damp and muddy section of the forest path. The path heads south
to a bend and towards what sounds like water, or east to drier parts.

name: On a muddy bank before the lake
description:
You find yourself on the banks of a large lake. Water sloshes at your feet and
the trees overhead hang heavily above it as if protecting the water. Around
the lake you can make out the figures of people fishing and talking. A path
heads north away from the river, or west to the edges of it.

name: On the edge of the fishing lake
description:
You are walking around the edge of a large lake filled with murky water.
The muddy path is slippery and hazardous but it hasn't prevented many people
from coming here to fish for their dinner. The lake heads north and west.

name: On the edge of the fishing lake
description:
You are walking around the edge of a large lake filled with murky water.
The muddy path is slippery and hazardous but it hasn't prevented many people
from coming here to fish for their dinner. The lake heads east and west.

name: On the edge of the fishing lake
description:
You are walking around the edge of a large lake filled with murky water.
The muddy path is slippery and hazardous but it hasn't prevented many people
from coming here to fish for their dinner. The lake heads north and east.

description:

description:

name: In a small outpost
description:
You are standing in a small wooden outpost designed for housing local guards
as they are sent to watch over people entering the dale from the south. The
room gives a good view of the bridge east and has arror slots for easy firing
at any invaders. There is very little else of interest here.

description:
You find yourself within a small but tidy house. The main room is large and
comfortable with a homely feeling about it. Small partitions seperate the
house into bedrooms and a couple of windows are set into the sides to provide
a view of the beautiful forests. There is a door leading north out of the
house.

name: Within the Dale inn
description:
You are standing in a smoke filled, noisy inn. Patrons stagger about and yell
to one another while other curse them and yell for them to go to the tavern
next door.

name: In a small grove
description:
You stand within a secluded grove of trees nestled between the farming fields
to the west and the forest around the dale. Dark shadows converge all around
and obscure your view of what lies beyond.

name: In a small grove
description:
You are within a quiet and dark grove nestled within the dale. Overhead the
trees cast deep and disturbing shadows upon you and obscure the pathway. All
around you the air seems very still.

name: In a small grove
description:
You are within a quiet and dark grove nestled within the dale. Overhead the
trees cast deep and disturbing shadows upon you and obscure the pathway. All
around you the air seems very still. To the east the grove seems very dark
and foreboding. Peering into it you can't make out anything, not even an end
to the trees...

name: In a small grove
description:
You are within a quiet and dark grove nestled within the dale. Overhead the
trees cast deep and disturbing shadows upon you and obscure the pathway. All
around you the air seems very still. All around you the grove seems to lead
into nothing but identical clearings.

name: Before a strange marble tower
description:
You are suddenly standing before a small tower made of marble. It is hard to
determine it's purpose since there are no windows of any sort and the only
distinguishing feature on it's smooth surface is an oak door leading east
into it. To the west you can see a dark and brooding grove.

name: Inside the marble tower
description:
The inside of the tower is even smaller than it looks on the outside. From
here it seems almost like a single room. You somehow get the feeling that it
is not normally like this, but is more a reaction to your prescence and that
you are unwanted here...there is an oak door leading west outside, and a
staircase leading up into the tower.

name: A small room in the marble tower
description:
You are within a tiny bare room. It seems that the tower is almost shrinking
as you go into it, as if trying to get rid of you. The only way out is a
door in the east wall.

name: Second floor of the marble tower
description:
You are in a small marble room which seems almost too small to be liveable.
Nothing is here at all, not even a window. You get a strange feeling you are
not wanted here, as if the tower is shrinking on you in order to make you
leave. Doors lie in the east and west walls, and a staircase heads up and
down through the tower.

name: A small room in the marble tower
description:
You are within a tiny bare room. It seems that the tower is almost shrinking
as you go into it, as if trying to get rid of you. The only way out is a
door in the west wall.

name: In a tiny room of the marble tower
description:
You stand in a tiny room of marble, barely large enough to stand in. The tower
almost seems to shrink as you go further into it, as if not wanting you here.
A staircase heads down and up, but the way up shrinks so severely that it is
quite impossible to go through it. There is a single door in the south wall
that seems to tingle with magic.

name: Darokin's Observation room
description:
This room is huge. Unlike the rest of the tower outside this room is built
for accomodation and comfort. The walls seem opaque and shimmer with magic
of incredible power. Very briefly images flicker across them, images of
places far away. The only exit is north out the door.

name: On the edge of the fishing lake
description:
You are walking around the edge of a large lake filled with murky water.
The muddy path is slippery and hazardous but it hasn't prevented many people
from coming here to fish for their dinner. To the east the lake heads onto
a narrow forest path.

name: In the ruins of the south gate
description:
You stand before a pile of rubble marking the entrance to what looked to once
be a fabulous elven city. Remains of what was once great still linger even
here in the rocks and creeping undergrowth. The shattered archway leading
into the city bears the markings of elvish highlords of longpast. To the
east and west you can make out rock strewn paths around the city
battlements. South of here heads into the dark forests.

name: In the ruins of the southern wall
description:
You are standing amidst the ruins of the great city. Large rocks have
fallen carelessly along the pathway and their absence from the walls is
plain from the large holes in it. A strong smell of decay is evident, and
the wind that whistles softly down the rocks is chilling.

plain from the large holes in it. A strong smell of decay is evident, and

name: On the remains of the battlement walls
description:
You are standing up on the rubbled remains of the city walls. The walls are
broken and rubbled, and the walkway around them is dangerous. Cold wind blows
over you and a dark shadow from the surrounding forest seems to cover
everything. The walkway heads east or back down to the ruined path of the
city's old walls.

description:

name: On the remains of the battlement walls
description:
The battlements here have totally collapsed. To the south the magnificent
stone walls have caved in to make an impassable pile of rubble seperating
this northern end of the wall from the southern. You can only head back
north.

south.

name: On the remains of the battlement walls
description:
You are standing up on the rubbled remains of the city walls. The walls are
broken and rubbled, and the walkway around them is dangerous. Cold wind blows
over you and a dark shadow from the surrounding forest seems to cover
everything. The walkway heads north and south.

name: On the remains of the battlement walls
description:
You are standing up on the rubbled remains of the city walls. The walls are
broken and rubbled, and the walkway around them is dangerous. Cold wind blows
over you and a dark shadow from the surrounding forest seems to cover
everything. The walkway heads north or you can go down to the rubbled ruins
of the city walls.

name: In the ruins of the southern courtyard
description:
The courtyard here is shattered and ruined after the devestation of some ages
past and long forgotten conflict. Rubble has fallen freely across the once
beautiful marble courts, and the stone fountain is dry and crumbling. To the
north lies the ruins of Myth Drannor. A large collapsed archway heads south
out of the city and toward the surrounding forest.

name: In the corner of the stone ruins
description:
You are within the rubbled remains of an ancient city. Plants and weeds have
grown across everything, and much of the time it almost seems as if the
forest is trying to bury the city into the past. The ground here is level
and reasonably flat, indicating that it was probably a market or common
area.

name: Swampy grounds amidst the ruins
description:
You are within the rubbled remains of an ancient city. Plants and weeds have
grown across everything, and much of the time it almost seems as if the
forest is trying to bury the city into the past. There is a lot of wet, damp
puddles of mud in the ground here, almost like a swamp was starting to form.

description:

name: Under a broken archway
description:
Above you is a majestic but shattered stone archway. Intricately carved signs
have been cut into it, and fine gems still lie embedded on it's surface. If
ever there was an indication of an abandoned city this is it, gems left here
untouched by even common looters and scavangers that usually haunt ruins. To
the east the ruins open out into a large open space filled with swampish weeds
and wet muddy gorund. In the distant north you can make out the ruins of some
towers.

name: Walking through the rubbled ruins
description:
You are amidst the ruins of the ancient elven city. All around you the stones
have been crushed and scattered, left to erode with time. The greatness that
was once here is long since gone and only the fine delicate stonework gives
any indication of what once was. The ruins wind north towards some towers, or
south to what appears to be a large broken archway.`

name: Walking through the rubbled ruins
description:
You are amidst the ruins of the ancient elven city. All around you the stones
have been crushed and scattered, left to erode with time. The greatness that
was once here is long since gone and only the fine delicate stonework gives
any indication of what once was. The ruins wind west and north towards some
towers.

name: Walking through the rubbled ruins
description:
You are amidst the ruins of the ancient elven city. All around you the stones
have been crushed and scattered, left to erode with time. The greatness that
was once here is long since gone and only the fine delicate stonework gives
any indication of what once was. The ruins wind north towards a junction.

name: Between the Towers of Passing
description:
You are standing in a large open space that appears almost as if maintained
and kept clear. The rubble and overgrown forest flora seems to have avoided
this region, and the destruction is more subdued here. Three towers lead off
from the square here: a green tinted one to the north, blue tinted to the
east and a blood red one to the west. The rubbled ruins lead southwards
away from here.

name: Before a tower of Blue tinged stone
description:
You are standing at the entrance to a small but conspicuous tower. Unlike
the rest of the ancient city this tower appears to be in almost perfect
condition. The wind here seems stilled and unnaturally quiet, not even the
sound of your own footsteps seems to reach your ears. A large stone door
tinged with some strange blue colour blocks the way east into the tower.

name: Before a tower of Green tinged stone
description:
You are standing at the entrance to a small but conspicuous tower. Unlike
the rest of the ancient city this tower appears to be in almost perfect
condition. The wind here seems stilled and unnaturally quiet, not even the
sound of your own footsteps seems to reach your ears. A large door made from
some green coloured stone is blocking the way north into the tower.

name: Before a tower of Red tinged stone
description:
You are standing at the entrance to a small but conspicuous tower. Unlike
the rest of the ancient city this tower appears to be in almost perfect
condition. The wind here seems stilled and unnaturally quiet, not even the
sound of your own footsteps seems to reach your ears. A large stone door
tinged with some strange red colour blocks the way west into the tower.

name: On a swampy part of the ruins
description:
The ruins here are overgrown with dark wet swamp growth. Thick wisps of foul
marsh gas rise up and hang in the air, almost burying the ruins beneath them.

name: On a crumbling bridge over a black river
description:
You stand on a wide but decayed stone bridge. Large portions of the span have
collapsed into the stagnant black waters beneath it, leaving huge holes that
threaten to swallow any who venture too close. To the south the ruins seem
to have become swamped with water and covered in marsh-like flora. North of
here there is a pile of rubbled ruins, most of which is impassable, but a
small section can be seen cleared away to allow some exploration.

name: In the ruins of an ancient city
description:
You are standing in the remains of a very old ruined city. The rubble here
is blasted and crushed beyond the power of anything you have ever seen before.
Around you thick bushes and trees have grown from between the cracks in the
stone ground, although nowhere near as much as would be expected from the time
that the city has been here.

name: Before a bloody signpost
description:
Here in the middle of the marshy ruins there is a large wooden sign covered in
dried blood and adorned with blackened and cracked skulls. The ruins to the
north of this sign seem ominous and less disturbed than to the west, and you
notice that almost all the tracks lead out from the north, rather than into it.

name: At a junction in the swampy ruins
description:
The wet marshlands that have grown here in the ruined elven city are almost
completely taking over the land. There is very little sign in this part of the
city of what once was, and the way through is blocked by the dense swamp muck
and deep holes of water. There is a wide, cleared path leading east, and a
darker path heading west. To the south the swamps seem to recede a little.

name: Walking through the swamp drowned ruins
description:
The ground here is like a normal swamp...wet, muddy and stinking. There is
almost no signs of the ancient city that once held power in this region, and
it's almost as if it never had been here. This swampy region is the most
blatantly obliterated part of the entire elven city.

name: Walking through the swamp drowned ruins
description:
The ground here is like a normal swamp...wet, muddy and stinking. There is
almost no signs of the ancient city that once held power in this region, and
it's almost as if it never had been here. This swampy region is the most
blatantly obliterated part of the entire elven city. The path heads north
and west, and to the east you can smell the faint smell of salty air.

name: Walking through the swamp drowned ruins
description:
The ground here is like a normal swamp...wet, muddy and stinking. There is
almost no signs of the ancient city that once held power in this region, and
it's almost as if it never had been here. This swampy region is the most
blatantly obliterated part of the entire elven city.

name: Walking through the swamp drowned ruins
description:
The ground here is like a normal swamp...wet, muddy and stinking. There is
almost no signs of the ancient city that once held power in this region, and
it's almost as if it never had been here. This swampy region is the most
blatantly obliterated part of the entire elven city. To the east you can make
out what looks like a raised clearing of rock above the swampy waters.

name: The residence of an Ancient Green dragon
description:
You stand upon a wide upraised part of the swamp. Large claw marks have been
scratched into the rocky surface of the rock and the burning smell of chlorine
fills the air.

name: In a quiet swampy part of the ruins
description:
The ruins here are almost buried by the swamp that has grown over it. Unlike
most of the ancient elven city this part seems to have been almost obliterated
by the destruction, leaving barely the smallest signs of what once was. There
is an unnerving stillness in this region.

name: In a quiet swampy part of the ruins
description:
The ruins here are almost buried by the swamp that has grown over it. Unlike
most of the ancient elven city this part seems to have been almost obliterated
by the destruction, leaving barely the smallest signs of what once was. There
is an unnerving stillness in this region.

description:

most of the ancient elven city this part seems to have been almost obliterated

is an unnerving stillness in this region. To the northeast you can see what
looks like a black tower standing within the swampy ruins.

name: In a quiet swampy part of the ruins
description:
The ruins here are almost buried by the swamp that has grown over it. Unlike
most of the ancient elven city this part seems to have been almost obliterated
by the destruction, leaving barely the smallest signs of what once was. There
is an unnerving stillness in this region. To the east you can see what looks
